<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Dev Learning Activation Email</title>
        <style type="text/css">
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                min-width: 100%;
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                background-color: #fafafa;
                color: #222222;
            }
            a {
                color: #000;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 1.25;
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 14px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            p {
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }
            table td {
                vertical-align: top;
            }
            .email-wrapper {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .email-header {
                background-color: #0078f3;
                padding: 24px;
                color: #fff;
            }
            .email-body {
                padding: 24px;
                background-color: #fff;
            }
            .email-footer {
                padding: 24px;
                background-color: #f6f6f6;
            }
            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                border-color: #0078f3;
                color: #fff;
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: 700;
                text-align: center;
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="email-header">
                <h1>Welcome to Dev Learning</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <%= user.name %></p>
                <p>Thank you for registering with Dev Learning. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
                <h2><%= activationCode%></h2>
                <p>Please enter th√≠ code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes</p>
                <p>If you did not register for a Dev Learning account, please ignore this email.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-footer">
                <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="">buihaibq9702@gmail.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>